			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 The system shall apply machine learning algorithms to sensor data to predict the likelihood, intensity, and potential impact zone of weather and tsunami events.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
			<reqID type="a">REQ_02</reqID>
		</IRequirement>
