			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 The system shall evaluate predefined thresholds for seismic activity, storm intensity, and water pressure, and generate alerts when thresholds are exceeded.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
